# Infrastructure Deployment Rules

## AWS CDK Setup
- Infrastructure code is located in `infrastructure/`
- Use TypeScript for CDK code
- Follow AWS best practices for resource naming and organization

## Deployment Guidelines
- Always test infrastructure changes in a development environment first
- Use environment-specific configurations (dev, staging, prod)
- Document all infrastructure changes in `docs/technical/`
- Ensure proper IAM roles and permissions are configured

## Resource Management
- Use CDK constructs for common patterns
- Tag all resources appropriately
- Follow least-privilege principle for IAM policies
- Document resource dependencies and relationships
